title: AVAILABLE NOW!! 2 BEDROOM, 1 BATH APT, OPEN FLOORPLAN
posting_body: 2 bedroom, 1 bath, open floorplan, Open kitchen w/granite counters, custom soft-close cabinets, SS appliances, breakfast bar and separate dining area.
Large 1 car garage w/built in storage, includes mudroom/laundry area just inside house from garage.

This house is in the good location, it’s close to Islandic Shopping Center, Hauppauge Shopping Center, and Hauppauge Plaza, rental fees including WIFI, Water, Electric, Laundry, Dishes cleaners, and toilet papers.
Beautifully landscaped yard includes private backyard w/stone pavers, water feature, covered patios front & back and storage shed.
